name: Janitor Prototype Beta
description:
Find the key, find the exit.

A and D to move left and right. Double press to dash.

Left Shift to push the bucket. Push hard into enemies for damage!

E to splash attack

Spacebar to jump

Hold F to use the bucket to replenish water, clean up dead rats for health, and activate switches.

Replenish buckets at Refill Stations by rolling the bucket under the spigot.

W and S raise and lower elevators
